race.comment: HARD COMPASS (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (24.57) last time in a Grade 5 at Bendigo. Cannot be left out. NEENA BALE (2) produced a moderate run last time when seventh at Geelong over 400m behind Forbes Lightning (23.43) in a Grade 5. Placed at her previous run. Should be about the money. PAW CASSIAN (5) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run. Something for the Multiples: ASTON JOPLIN (10)
